{"tid":88313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我既願望係喺情人節收到一大棵西蘭花","createTime":"2017-01-20T13:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T14:09:59.000Z","uid":77826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d99f3290ecb4160ed2ffffdeba0778f29832e2e9","tid":88313,"uid":77826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"情人節大多女仔都想收到花<br />\n覺得好浪漫<br />\n但係我好想喺成條街個個女仔都拎住一束花既時候<br />\n我可以拎住一大束西蘭花<br />\n因為我真係覺得<strong>好型</strong>🤔🤔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/20/215715_26573e2c4355c2ff4a223042bec16578.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F20%2F215715_26573e2c4355c2ff4a223042bec16578.jpg&h=89e06471&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大概係咁<br />\n不過最好係一大個 <br />\n因為細細個可能會跌出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba9a5ff7b4f85b5b7637c7fb66a600fc5fead1b1","tid":88313,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"我推薦你一拎椰菜花，又好意頭，又有新意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a205eabc2f4af8493771f79b13ba7aa64c57fe45","tid":88313,"uid":54049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我推薦你一拎椰菜花，又好意頭，又有新意！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}